Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:58.69,OPTitle,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\be3}{\pos(492,290)}「散華…禮彌」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:09.68,EDTitle,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be7}{\pos(320,250)}「普通的…女孩子…」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------TEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.58,0:00:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳是不是有點瘸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  剛才腳滑的時候扭到的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒事的  只是回家的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等  你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  你摸哪兒吶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.38,0:00:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家的路上  我們互相都沒有說什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在到底在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後希望做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該聽她傾訴一下才比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事後回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候可能是拯救她的最後一次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:02:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膚淺的女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我沒有發現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後不會再讓你出門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不再讓你去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你見任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}不需要什麼朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}你只要有我就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這藥  來結束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}你只要有我在就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒能死成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親  母親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早上好  禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不遵守規定  晚上偷偷溜出去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  母親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  月亮實在是太美麗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想去享受森林浴  就不由得…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  給我注意點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行為會影響到我的評價的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對禮彌用這種說法也太過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親  您不用餐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌  昨天真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然那樣打你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我不對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的是很感謝父親您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌  能夠保護你的就只有我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼穿著制服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過你這段時間就在家裡自習的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團一郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌  你去換衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道些什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  關於昨晚的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個少年的身份已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紫陽高中的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二丁目的那個寺院住持的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道在說降谷君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓他不能再接近禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他「去勢」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷君有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了復活藥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓死去的小巴布喝了下去  你在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你好歹也是寺院住持的兒子  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧萌路  真是懷疑他的倫理觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我知道哥他從以前開始就是喜歡殭屍的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著惡趣味的大變態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟然會做到這種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了  輪不到你來說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  確實我可能是做了件讓人噁心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布真的就這樣復活了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  難道你不高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布復活了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  我確實也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是真的復活什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽吧  那個特殊的像是鼻音的叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是正宗的巴布啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖這麼說  果然那個還是覺得有點怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}巴布…  快點下來吧  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且眼珠還在發光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  之前感覺更有感情什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是特徵沒有什麼改變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說會有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊  如果真的復活了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像殭屍那樣襲擊人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能保證被咬的人就不會被變成殭屍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能  這種像漫畫一樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的敢百分百保證嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  哥  書包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  今天我蹺課
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎麼了  發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺  哥說什麼他把巴布復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要再養隻別的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦吼  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布復活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈  真是太好太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時都很容易就讓我抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你  直接用手抓會不會有危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸子姐姐啊  你不是還有晨練嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有作為姐姐  監督千紘的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是表姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  爬進那種地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  你要爬進去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就被好好的折騰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好長啊  根本看不到盡頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要擦到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這洞到底通到哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股卡住了  爬不過去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小巴布是很重要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微也在意一下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽得到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  千紘你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到出口了  咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的…下面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  茂木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}一年五班  康孝  性別·帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡棒球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  嗯  只是看的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只是看的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才不發育啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞這裡舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對茂木性騷擾也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究就是個茂木而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊  康孝君  不知道你在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個果然還是應該是散女的大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想請問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  降…降谷君在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降…降
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找一年級的降谷千紘君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降…千…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎  茂木君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  好像  今天還沒來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找…找那傢伙有什麼事嗎  有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要被去勢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  剛剛從大小姐的嘴裡…  去…去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不  非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會這麼關心降谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我沒說什麼奇怪的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷君會在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  你說禮彌在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  先讓她走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在後面跟好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  巴布跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸子那傢伙也沒跟上來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼監督義務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好  快下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃紫陽花的葉子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下  這裡難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  是昨天那傢伙逞強爬的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  咦  為什麼她在這個時候會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一直去的廢棄旅館裡等著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:15:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定能見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到那裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想因為自己的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而給降谷君添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要去哪裡啊  禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林浴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話是不是走得有點遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰  難道說那就是禮彌的父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  回去吧  現在回去還能原諒你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個很聰明的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是散華家的女兒  我的女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:17:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  剛才的行為是怎麼回事  禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實是你的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這並不代表
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身心都是你的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一點就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我自由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這具體是什麼樣的自由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想要外出的自由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…  戀愛的自由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  請等一下  父親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就今天  就今天就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  反正肯定是要見那個叫降谷的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼啊  這髒兮兮的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…巴布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下  別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會過敏的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小巴布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然真的復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  不可以碰它  會被弄髒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說那之後降谷君把藥完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個藥其實是已經完成了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌  讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  父親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  回話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…竟然真的死了  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多開不起玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我復活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  我  做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷…君…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降…谷君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還沒讓你喝藥  為…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦  神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團…團一郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷…君…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像約定的那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請負起責任來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.48,0:21:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.54,0:23:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,添了不少麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.42,0:23:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過問題解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和寫這個的人見了面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的和他聊過了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:23:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  散華禮彌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:24:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四話  「普通的…女孩子…」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.26,0:24:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要看哦萌路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也接受那邊的意思了  不會再迷茫了


